That's, you know, I
cannot talk about that.

00:32:24.440 --> 00:32:27.670
Yes. Oh, he's going to
ask why my name is Hank.

00:32:27.670 --> 00:32:28.970
I knew it.

00:32:28.970 --> 00:32:30.270
Okay.

00:32:30.270 --> 00:32:32.940
&gt;&gt; No. I'm going to
