&gt;&gt; Hello. As just considering
from a writing perspective,

00:37:37.730 --> 00:37:42.760
do you think it would be better
or advantageous to be living

00:37:42.760 --> 00:37:45.160
with a prosecutor versus
a defense attorney?

00:37:45.160 --> 00:37:48.850
&gt;&gt; Hank Phillippi Ryan: Do
I think it would be better

00:37:48.850 --> 00:37:51.580
to be living with a
prosecutor or defense attorney,

00:37:51.580 --> 00:37:53.630
from the standpoint
of writing a novel?

00:37:53.630 --> 00:37:56.330
Yes. Two hilarious
things about that

00:37:56.330 --> 00:37:58.100
and that is the funniest
question I've ever heard

00:37:58.100 --> 00:38:00.160
and you'll hear why.

